íŸ@2d0266fe665241977ac8e8cb5770b5376d1e17c93a8b8352b091e173323bf16e⁄‚Title: title: math variance
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the variance of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3 4 5] | math variance
2.0

```
Get the sample variance of a list of numbers.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3 4 5] | math variance --sample
2.5

```
Compute the variance of each column in a table.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [1 2] [3 4]] | math variance
